<h1>Keyboard Shortcuts</h1>

<p>
  GuitarGeeksVR is mainly controlled by head gestures.
  For advanced functionality (or if you even prefer using the keyboard) the following shortcuts are available:
</p>

<table class="tg">
  <tr>
    <td class="alignC"><kbd>ENTER</kbd></td>
    <td>Recenter HMD (this is probably required once after startup)</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="alignC"><kbd>SPACE</kbd></td>
    <td>Start/stop playback</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="alignC"><kbd>LEFT</kbd> / <kbd>RIGHT</kbd></td>
    <td>Seek forward/backward</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="alignC"><kbd>UP</kbd> / <kbd>DOWN</kbd></td>
    <td>Rotate fretboard</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="alignC"><kbd>TAB</kbd></td>
    <td>Cycle through scene configurations</td>
  </tr>
</table>

